{
  "stem": "17301.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 117.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, in the meantime, by the time we went to Neustadt-Glewe, my sister was very weak, lost an awful lot of weight.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother was very, very weak, and also, lost a an awful lot of weight.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they couldn't really put in a good day's work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the very first job we had was dig trenches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they told us how long and how wide.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we start to dig trenches.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was hard work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I-- I was the strongest of-- of us three.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I dug.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I finished what I was-- I was supposed to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then I went over and I helped my mother and my sister, because when-- when we went out to dig trenches, there weren't that many SS officers with us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was mostly Wehrmacht, you know, from the regular German army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I got lucky because one of the Wehrmacht that was watching me dig the trench came over and-- and start to talk to me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says to me, where are you from?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I says, I'm from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, oh, I'm from Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, oh, well, then we are not too far from each other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, that's right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we started talk, and he befriended me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what he did for me, he says to me, tomorrow when you come tomorrow, he says, would you like a baked potato?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I says, I would love it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I would love it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he made a baked potato for me next day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I hid it under my coat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When I-- when-- and when we went back in, in the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, that went on for a few days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After about a week or so, my mother got really very, very weak, and my sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
